Heaven has a new Angel . I'm so sad that my amazing friend @nickchavezbh has gone to heaven . Nick was the kindest , most fun, caring, loving and loyal friend anybody could ever hope to have and the best keeper of my most personal secrets . He went out of his way to support you emotionally with all the ups and downs of life in such a beautiful and meaningful way. He was also such a generous connector of people and wanted to help people meet all the right people . I will miss Nick so much and all our special conversations. He was also the best , most talented and meticulous hair dresser and made every person who came to him look the best that they have ever looked. He was also the king of @tvsn and @qvc selling his incredible line of hair products which are the best of the best  @nickchavezbeverlyhills . My heart hurts deeply knowing I won't see him again . Sending so much love to Nicks amazing sisters who so lovingly took care of him through this tough 3 year journey with pancreatic cancer which Nick fought so valiantly #heavenhasanewangel #endpancreaticcancer  #angelinheaven #purelove #purefriendship

Dream team of research scientists, generous sponsors , and the most loving, loyal and supportive friends at the 30th annual @racetoerasems kick off lunch hosted by the phenomenal and brand new @steak48 . When we started this important journey there were no medicines , treatments and no hope for people like me who have MS . Miraculously and with so much hard work and prayers there are now 25 FDA approved drugs to help stop the progression of MS. For someone diagnosed today the future is bright but we still have a long way to go to win The Race To Erase MS @janesiskin @ltlindathompson @@devinenews @nbtt @judybswartz @maryjohausman @cinqasept @janesiskin @kymdouglas @kurtthecyberguy @dorothy_lucey @lillylee15266 @siedahgarrett @lisastanley30 Plan to come to 30th annual The Race To Erase on June 2 @fairmontcenturyplaza hotel . 3 years ago today my love , my son , my Prince, my Angel , the biggest piece of my heart ♥️ Jason went to heaven. On Jasons 3rd Angelversary I send him all the love I have in my heart. I always wish and pray that I could have at least one more day with him to tell him just how much I love him , how much his life mattered to so many, how proud I was of him, what a big difference he made in this world, how he made me feel and that he will just walk in the door and give me one of his famous teddy bear hugs and that this terrible gut wrenching pain in my heart could just go away . I miss every unique and exquisite detail of Jason, his life , the true love he had in his heart for everyone, the beautiful hours of music he brought to our home and all the endless laughter and especially his giving heart and love for creating charities and giving back first to @racetoerasems then co creating @cureaddictionnow . I know you are guiding me and your sisters from heaven to develop real cures for addiction with CAN which you were so proud to create and save lives . We are all working really hard with your beautiful guidance to make CAN the success you dreamed it would be and are going to make your beautiful dream come true. I love you forever Jason and am so grateful for the honor I had of being your mom.
I cherish all the beautiful memories I hold in my heart of you . @jasondavis3606 @nataliecoleofficial @brandondavis1111 @isabella_rickel @marielladr_ @kenny_rickel @davisknoll1 @dochollywoodnft  #heavenhasmyangel #heavenhasmyheart @cureaddictionnow #cureaddictionnow #hugsfromheaven #sunsetsfromheaven

Heaven has a new Angel. My beautiful sister Patty Raynes @praynes went to heaven yesterday. I'm beyond shocked and devastated to lose my fun, loving, loyal and caring sister with no warning and not getting to give her one last kiss, one last hug and one last time of telling her how much I really loved her and how important she was to me and so loved by so many who were lucky enough to know her. I will always hold her in the most special place in my heart and treasure these and so many beautiful memories we have shared . There was nobody like Patty and she really knew how to make you feel so loved . I know she is now with her son Nicholas embracing him as she was so sad always about him leaving this earth too soon in life and on a big horse farm in heaven jumping over beautiful clouds and tall fences #heavenhasanewangel #heavenhasmyheart #heartbroken💔 #sisterlove #sisterhood

Rest in Peace & Love , my beautiful, fun ,extraordinary and loving sister Patty Raynes . We had a beautiful and meaningful service to celebrate @praynes life yesterday at @jeanshafiroff home . I will miss her so much and picture her in heaven today with her son Nicholas and my son Jason in a warm and loving embrace and soaring over heavenly pillowy clouds on her horse with gorgeous sunsets like the one pictured here which was waiting when I arrived in NY. #heavenhasanewangel #heavenhasmysister #sisterlove #rip @matthew_raynes @davisknoll1 @isabella_rickel @jasondavis3606 @nisijoy @michelerella1 @cureaddictionnow @tonya_winfield

Happy Mothers Day to my mom , my heart , my first love of my life Barbara Davis @davisknoll1 . My mom embodies the true deepest meaning of love and has always been there from the day I was born to love me , support me in every possible way , to educate me, empower me, make me feel loved and supported and inspire me to challenge myself and have the confidence to do anything in life that was truly meaningful . She is my absolute everything and has taught me the importance of charity and just how rewarding it is to dedicate your life to giving back . I am the luckiest woman in the world to be able to call Barbara Davis my mom , my best friend, my hero , the person I look up to more than anybody in the world and for my children to be able to call her grandma and enjoy the most heartfelt and beautiful relationship and my husband @kenny_rickel to call her his mother in law . She is the most involved and loving grandmother who loves her grandchildren with all her heart and is so beautifully involved daily in the most special way calling them daily and taking so much delight in their lives and making them feel surrounded in love . Mothers Day was created for mothers like you . I thank God every day for you and our beautiful and loving relationship . I love you forever with every piece of my heart ❤️ #happymothersday #bestmotherintheworld #momlife #myheart

Happy 30th Anniversary @marksgarden , @michael_marksgarden and Richard and Mark and thank-you for these breathtakingly gorgeous flowers you sent me to commemorate your 30th Anniversary in business. You deserve to celebrate the evolution of your most spectacular and meaningful business. Everything you create is so elegant and beautiful and feels so warm and wonderful to have in your home. I found you 29 years ago when I was planning my wedding as I had you and several other florists set up a sample table in my home to see who could create the essence of my vision and yours was the most amazing and superior to anything I had ever seen. You did my wedding in the most beautiful, breathtaking and memorable way then and thus began our almost 30 year spectacular relationship with you creating the most beautiful highlight reel of my life creating and donating all the spectacular flowers for The Race To Erase MS events doing all my families Bar and Bat Mitzvahs, wedding and baby showers , baby arrivals , birthdays , anniversaries, mothers days holiday celebrations and every important milestone event in my life . When my son @jasondavis3606 passed away you created the most peaceful and beautiful flowers to celebrate his life and still send flowers every week . There is nothing you can't do and are quite simply the best of the best and I'm so grateful for you and our special friendship and want to celebrate and toast you on this fabulous milestone in your lives.
Peace & Love #30thanniversary

Breaking news ! On the eve of World Overdose Day tomorrow , August 31 the exciting news just came out today from Exigent that their drug Narcan or Nalaxone is now available over the counter in pharmacies and grocery stores all over the country from @exigentsolutions . @cureaddictionnow we have strongly been advocating for this for the last 2 years for opiod overdoses which include @fentanyl , heroin and OxyContin as this is the only way to save a life by carrying this with you everywhere you go to reverse the effects of an overdose . For overdoses you have 4 minutes until brain damage sets in and 6 minutes until you die. If you call 911 it takes on a average 10 minutes to arrive . You can’t afford not to have this on you and learn how to use it. Every teenager should also take this with them in their backpacks or purses for school and definitely when going out at night . Every parent , Uber or Lyft , taxi , bus or limo driver must carry this on them at all times It’s a matter of life and death 💀 Please come to our @cureaddictionnow Forum and webinar on September 15 at @fairmontcenturyplaza at 9:00 AM to learn more about this and all the latest SUD research from our incredible team of research scientists and we will be giving out Narcan #cureaddictionnow #stopfentanylnow #stopfentanyldeaths #stopfentanylpoisoning . @jasonwahler @isabella_rickel @lawrencezarian @jasondavis3606 @dr.scaligiuri @kurtdras “Courtesy of Emergent” @worldoverdose #worldoverdoseday #stopoverdose
